---
description: SourceDraft CMS project rules
alwaysApply: true
---

This is an open-source Git-based CMS for Markdown/MDX publishing.

Do not build a generic SaaS dashboard.
Do not hardcode QuBrite-specific logic into the core.
Do not expose tokens or secrets in browser code.
Do not create fake analytics, fake charts, fake placeholder features, or generic dashboard bloat.
Do not add unnecessary comments explaining obvious code.
Do not refactor unrelated files.
Use a universal article schema.
Use adapters for publishing targets.
First adapter: Astro MDX.
Future adapters: Next.js MDX, Hugo Markdown, WordPress API, and Ghost API.
Keep code typed, small, readable, and testable.
Every module should have a clear purpose.
Prefer boring reliable code over clever abstractions.
